=== 反应 ===
金刚烷的多数反应在桥头碳上发生(主环的1,3,5,7位),这与桥头[[碳正离子|碳正离子]]的C<sub>sp<sup>3</sup></sub>-C<sub>sp<sup>3</sup></sub>轨道与p轨道发生了[[超共轭|超共轭]]有关<ref>{{cite journal| title= First Crystal Structure Analysis of an Aliphatic Carbocation—Stabilization of the 3,5,7-Trimethyl-1-adamantyl Cation by C-C Hyperconjugation| author=Laute T.| journal = Angew. Chem. | volume = 25 | year = 1986 | pages = 348-350 | doi= 10.1002/anie.198603491}}</ref>。

==== 氧化 ====
金刚烷与浓[[硫酸|硫酸]]反应，生成[[2-金刚烷酮|2-金刚烷酮]] <ref>{{cite journal |doi=10.15227/orgsyn.053.0008|title=Adamantanone|first1=H. W.|last1=Geluk|first2=V. G.|last2=Keizer|journal=Organic Syntheses|year=1973|volume=53|page=8}}</ref>。
[[File:Adamantanone_synthesis.png|center]]
金刚烷酮的[[羰基|羰基]]有助于合成某些衍生物，如2-金刚烷甲腈<ref>[http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/prep.asp?prep=cv6p0041 2-Adamantanecarbonitrile] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120710204357/http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/prep.asp?prep=cv6p0041 |date=2012-07-10 }} Organic Syntheses, Coll. Vol. 6, p. 41 (1988); Vol. 57, p. 8 (1977).</ref>和2-甲基金刚烷<ref>{{Cite journal
| title= The Preparation and Reactivity of 2-Substituted Derivatives of Adamantane
|author1=Schleyer P. R. |author2=Nicholas R. D. | journal = [[J._Am._Chem._Soc.|J. Am. Chem. Soc.]]
| volume = 83
| issue = 1
| year = 1961
| pages = 182–187
| doi= 10.1021/ja01462a036}}</ref>。

1-羟基金刚烷可以通过1-溴金刚烷在[[丙酮|丙酮]]水溶液中水解而来，也可以直接通过金刚烷的[[臭氧化反应|臭氧化反应]]产生<ref>Zvi Cohen, Haim Varkony, Ehud Keinan, and Yehuda Mazur [http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/prep.asp?prep=cv6p0043 Tertiary alcohols from hydrocarbons by ozonation on silica gel: 1-adamantanol] Organic Syntheses, Coll. Vol. 6, p. 43 (1988); Vol. 59, p. 176 (1979)</ref>：
[[File:1-Adamantanol_synthesis.png|center]]

==== 卤化 ====
金刚烷非常容易发生[[亲电取代反应|亲电取代反应]]，可以通过控制反应条件来影响产物的组成<ref Name="msu_pr"/>。
[[File:Adamantane_bromination.png|center]]

将金刚烷与[[溴|溴]]煮沸可以得到单取代产物，向其中添加路易斯酸催化剂则可以实现多次取代<ref Name="nesmeyanov">{{cite book|author =Nesmeyanov, A. N.|title=Basic organic chemistry|language =ru|year=1969|page=664}}</ref>。溴代的速率在加入路易斯酸后变快，且在{{le|辐照|irradiation}}或添加[[自由基|自由基]]时没有变化，证明反应是通过离子进行的<ref Name="cr64" />。

最开始金刚烷的氟化是以1-羟基金刚烷<ref>{{cite journal| title= Pyridinium poly (hydrogen fluoride): a convenient reagent for organic fluorination reactions|author =Olah, George A.| journal = Journal of Organic Chemistry| volume = 44|issue = 22| year = 1979| pages = 3872–3881| doi= 10.1021/jo01336a027| last2= Welch| first2= John T.| last3= Vankar| first3= Yashwant D.| last4= Nojima| first4= Mosatomo| last5= Kerekes| first5= Istvan| last6= Olah| first6= Judith A.}}</ref>和1-氨基金刚烷作为起始反应物进行的，后来能够从金刚烷直接氟代<ref>{{Cite journal| title= Ionic fluorination of adamantane, diamantane, and triphenylmethane with nitrosyl tetrafluoroborate/pyridine polyhydrogen fluoride (PPHF)| author=Olah, George A.| journal = Journal of Organic Chemistry| volume = 48| issue = 19| year = 1983| pages = 3356–3358| doi= 10.1021/jo00167a050| last2= Shih| first2= Joseph G.| last3= Singh| first3= Brij P.| last4= Gupta| first4= B. G. B.}}</ref>。在所有情况下，反应都是先形成碳正离子，然后与氟化的亲核试剂反应得到。也有报告使用气态氟直接氟代金刚烷的研究<ref>{{Cite journal| title= Direct synthesis of fluoro-bicyclic compounds with fluorine| author=Rozen, Shlomo.| journal = Journal of Organic Chemistry| volume = 53| issue = 12| year = 1988| pages = 2803–2807| doi=10.1021/jo00247a026| last2= Gal| first2= Chava}}</ref>。

==== 羧基化 ====
金刚烷的羧基化反应在1960年首次被报道，使用[[甲酸|甲酸]]作羧化剂，[[四氯化碳|四氯化碳]]作溶剂<ref>{{cite journal|author1=Koch, H.  |author2=Haaf, W. |title=Direkte Synthese der Adamantan-carbonsäure-(1)|journal=Angewandte Chemie|volume=72|issue=17|pages=628|doi=10.1002/ange.19600721710|year=1960|bibcode=1960AngCh..72..628K }}</ref>。
[[File:Adamantane_caboxylic_acid_synthesis.png|center]]

[[叔丁醇|叔丁醇]]和硫酸帮助产生金刚烷阳离子，随后利用甲酸和硫酸的作用下产生的[[一氧化碳|一氧化碳]]，将阳离子原位羧化<ref name="cr64" />。羧化反应产物的比例为55-60%<ref Name="carboxylation">[http://www.orgsyn.org/orgsyn/prep.asp?prep=cv5p0020 1-Adamantanecarboxylic acid] Organic Syntheses, Coll. Vol. 5, p. 20 (1973); Vol. 44, p. 1 (1964).</ref>。

