== 用途 ==
未经官能团修饰的金刚烷本身少有应用，可以用于聚合物或{{le|干法蚀刻|dry etching}}模具<ref>{{cite web|author =Watanabe, Keiji |year=2001 |title=Resist Composition and Pattern Forming Process |work=United States Patent Application 20010006752 |publisher=Bandwidth Market, Ltd |url=http://www.bandwidthmarket.com/resources/patents/apps/ |access-date=14 October 2005 |display-authors=etal |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110904234140/http://www.bandwidthmarket.com/resources/patents/apps/ |archive-date=September 4, 2011 }}</ref>。

固态NMR光谱中，金刚烷可以作为化学位移值参考的标准<ref>{{cite journal|author1=Morcombe, Corey R. |author2=Zilm, Kurt W. | title= Chemical Shift referencing in MAS solid state NMR|journal= J. Magn. Reson.|year= 2003|volume= 162|pages= 479–486 |doi= 10.1016/S1090-7807(03)00082-X|pmid= 12810033|issue= 2|bibcode = 2003JMagR.162..479M }}</ref>。

在[[染料激光器|染料激光器]]中，金刚烷可用于延长增益介质的使用寿命；它不能在大气中被[[光电离|光电离]]，因为它的吸收谱带在真空紫外区<ref>{{cite journal|author1=Lenzke, K. |author2=Landt, L. |author3=Hoener, M. |s2cid=3131583 |title= Experimental determination of the ionization potentials of the first five members of the nanodiamond series|journal= J. Chem. Phys.|year= 2007|volume= 127|issue= 8|pmid= 17764261|pages= 084320 |doi= 10.1063/1.2773725|display-authors=etal|bibcode = 2007JChPh.127h4320L }}</ref>。

=== 药物用途 ===
迄今为止，未发现金刚烷的医学用途，但其许多衍生物都被用作合成药物。第一个用于医学用途的金刚烷衍生物是金刚烷胺，在1967年用作抗病毒药物<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1126/science.386515|title=Panel urges wide use of antiviral drug|year=1979|last1=Maugh|first1=T.|journal=Science|volume=206|pages=1058–60|pmid=386515|issue=4422|bibcode = 1979Sci...206.1058M }}</ref>，随后还被用于治疗[[帕金森病|帕金森病]] <ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=TdcXatjup5cC&pg=PA87|page=87|title=The Complete Pill Guide: Everything You Need to Know about Generic and Brand-Name Prescription Drugs|author =Sonnberg, Lynn |publisher=Barnes & Noble Publishing|year=2003|isbn=0-7607-4208-1}}</ref><ref name="pmid15800186">{{cite journal |vauthors=Blanpied TA, Clarke RJ, Johnson JW |title=Amantadine inhibits NMDA receptors by accelerating channel closure during channel block |journal=Journal of Neuroscience |volume=25 |issue=13 |pages=3312–22 |year=2005 |pmid=15800186 |pmc=6724906 |doi=10.1523/JNEUROSCI.4262-04.2005 }}</ref>。其他的衍生物药物有诸如[[阿达帕林|阿达帕林]]、{{le|阿达普洛明|adapromine}}、{{le|布罗曼丹|bromantane}}、[[卡金刚酸|卡金刚酸]]、多巴金刚、[[美金刚胺|美金刚胺]]、[[金刚乙胺|金刚乙胺]]、[[沙格列汀|沙格列汀]]、{{le|曲金刚胺|tromantadine}}、[[维格列汀|维格列汀]]等。金刚烷类似物的聚合物已经获得专利，用作抗[[HIV|HIV]]的抗病毒剂<ref>{{Cite web
