=== 航天燃料 ===
金刚烷是[[霍尔效应推进器|霍尔效应推进器]]的有力候选者，因为其易于离子化、便于以固态储存、在相对较低的温度下升华和低毒性（相对于其他燃料而言）<ref name="ais">{{cite web
|url=https://appliedionsystems.com/portfolio/ais-eht1-micro-end-hall-thruster/
|title=AIS-EHT1 Micro End Hall Thruster - Applied Ion Systems
|access-date = 2021-02-22
|language=en
}}</ref>。

=== 潜在应用 ===
金刚烷的某些烷基衍生物被用作[[液压|液压系统]]中的工作溶液<ref Name="krugosvet">{{cite web
| url= http://www.krugosvet.ru/enc/nauka_i_tehnika/himiya/ADAMANTAN.html
| title= Adamantane
| access-date = 2009-11-11
| language =ru
| work = Krugosvet
| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20091106115230/http://www.krugosvet.ru/enc/nauka_i_tehnika/himiya/ADAMANTAN.html| archive-date= 6 November 2009 | url-status= live}}</ref>。金刚烷基的聚合物可能会应用于[[触摸屏|触摸屏]]涂层<ref>{{Cite journal|title= Synthesis and characterization of the first adamantane-based poly (p-phenylenevinylene) derivative: an intelligent plastic for smart electronic displays| author=Jeong, H. Y.| journal = Thin Solid Films| volume = 417| issue = 1–2| year = 2002| pages = 171–174| doi= 10.1016/S0040-6090(02)00569-2| bibcode=2002TSF...417..171J}}</ref>，在[[纳米技术|纳米技术]]中金刚烷及其[[同系物|同系物]]也具有发展前景。例如，金刚烷固体的软性笼状结构能够笼络客体分子，并且可以在[[基质|基质]]被破坏时将其释放到人体内<ref name=app/><ref>{{Cite book |title   = Diamondoids as Molecular Building Blocks for Nanotechnology |author1 = Ramezani, Hamid |author2 = Mansoori, G. Ali |volume  = 109 |year  = 2007 |pages   = [https://archive.org/details/molecularbuildin0000unse/page/44 44–71] |doi     = 10.1007/978-0-387-39938-6_4 |series  = Topics in Applied Physics |isbn    = 978-0-387-39937-9 |url     = https://archive.org/details/molecularbuildin0000unse/page/44}}</ref>。金刚烷可用作分子晶体[[自组装|自组装]]的[[分子砌块|分子砌块]]<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Markle|first1=R. C.|title=Molecular building blocks and development strategies for molecular nanotechnology|journal=Nanotechnology|date=2000|volume=11|issue=2|pages=89–99|doi=10.1088/0957-4484/11/2/309|bibcode=2000Nanot..11...89M}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Garcia|first1=J. C.|last2=Justo|first2=J. F.|last3=Machado|first3=W. V. M.|last4=Assali|first4=L. V. C.|title=Functionalized adamantane: building blocks for nanostructure self-assembly|journal=Phys. Rev. B|date=2009|volume=80|issue=12|page=125421|doi=10.1103/PhysRevB.80.125421|bibcode=2009PhRvB..80l5421G|arxiv = 1204.2884 |s2cid=118828310}}</ref>。

== 金刚烷类似物 ==
许多分子、离子都有着类金刚烷的笼状结构，例如[[三氧化二磷|P<sub>4</sub>O<sub>6</sub>]]、[[三氧化二砷|As<sub>4</sub>O<sub>6</sub>]]、[[五氧化二磷|P<sub>4</sub>O<sub>10</sub>]]、[[五硫化二磷|P<sub>4</sub>S<sub>10</sub>]]和[[乌洛托品|乌洛托品]]<ref>{{cite journal|author = Vitall, J. J.|title = The Chemistry of Inorganic and Organometallic Compounds with Adamantane-Like Structures|journal = Polyhedron|year = 1996|volume = 15|pages = 1585–1642|doi = 10.1016/0277-5387(95)00340-1|issue = 10}}</ref>。特别是[[四亚甲基二砜四胺|四亚甲基二砜四胺]]（TETS），俗称毒鼠强，对人类有着极大的毒性。金刚烷的[[硅|硅]]系类似物{{NoteTag|sila-adamantane}}在2005年被合成，这是一种含有金刚烷结构的有机硅笼化合物<ref>{{Cite journal
