ild | journal = Organometallics | year = 2010 | volume = 29 | issue = 1 | pages = 32–33 | doi = 10.1021/om900998q | title = Arsenicin A, A Natural Polyarsenical: Synthesis and Crystal Structure| hdl = 1885/58485 | hdl-access = free }}</ref>。

